rs will likely make relatively simple, transparent proposals that promise clear gains to at least one counterpart and allow quick inference about others’ types. Given the proposer schedule and personas, peacock is likely to be the main driver of trade, pushing multi-chip red acquisitions funded by green, while otter and badger accept selectively when offered immediate, clear gains without excessive risk of being exploited or left with clearly inferior portfolios.",
