rs. Across the three rounds, we should expect early cautious, green-anchored proposals, then a move toward exploiting purple’s divergence in value (Dog values it most; Buffalo least), and finally some riskier or more grabby attempts before the game ends, with acceptance decisions primarily driven by immediate value gains rather than long-term norms.",
